OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,FManchester United youngster Jack
OL,7,FFletcher has apologised for using a
OL,8,Fhomophobic slur during an EFL Trophy
OL,9,Fmatch after being handed a six-game
OL,10,Fban.
OL,12,FThe 18-year-old, who is the son of
OL,13,Fformer United midfielder and current
OL,14,Fcoach Darren Fletcher, was sent off in
OL,15,Fthe incident, which occurred in a
OL,16,Fclash against Barnsley in October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
