CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772712216
OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,FFletcher was heard by the referee
OL,7,Fdirecting the term "gay boy" at an
OL,8,Fopponent, with a regulatory commission
OL,9,Fhearing deciding he had used it as an
OL,10,Finsult.
OL,12,FThe teenager said on manutd.com: "I am
OL,13,Ftruly sorry for the offensive word
OL,14,Fthat I used in the heat of the moment.
OL,16,F"Despite the fact that I had no
OL,17,Fintention to use the term as a
OL,18,Fhomophobic insult, I completely
OL,19,Funderstand that such language is
OL,20,Funacceptable and immediately
OL,21,Fapologised after the game.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@\O]tD@bOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
