PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772712216
OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,F"I want to be clear that this
OL,7,Fmomentary lapse of character
OL,8,Fabsolutely does not reflect my beliefs
OL,9,For values."
OL,11,FA statement from United read:
OL,12,F"Manchester United has worked with
OL,13,FJack to strengthen his understanding
OL,14,Fof discriminatory language and why it
OL,15,Fis harmful."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
