CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772712216
OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,F"In addition to his ongoing
OL,7,Fparticipation in regular academy
OL,8,Fprogrammes on diversity and inclusion,
OL,9,FJack will also take part in
OL,10,Feducational training through the FA
OL,11,F(Football Association).
OL,13,F"Manchester United prides itself on
OL,14,Fbeing an inclusive and welcoming club.
OL,15,FSince launching All Red All Equal in
OL,16,F2016, we have embedded equality,
OL,17,Fdiversity and inclusion into
OL,18,Feverything we do."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@RO]
