PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772712216
OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,FAs well as missing an EFL Trophy match
OL,7,Ffollowing the red card, Fletcher was
OL,8,Fsuspended for four non-first team
OL,9,Fcontests, of which he has sat out
OL,10,Fthree, with a further match also to be
OL,11,Fserved.
OL,13,FFletcher has also been fined #1,500
OL,14,Fand ordered to attend a mandatory face-
OL,15,Fto-face education programme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
