PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772712216
OL,3,CMan Utd's Jack Fletcher apologises for
OL,4,Chomophobic slur
OL,6,FThe teenager, who joined United in
OL,7,F2023 from Manchester City along with
OL,8,Fhis twin brother Tyler, has made three
OL,9,Fappearances in the Premier League this
OL,10,Fseason as a substitute and is
OL,11,Fconsidered one of the club's brightest
OL,12,Fprospects.
OL,14,FA statement on social media from
OL,15,FRainbow Devils, United's LGBTQ+
OL,16,Fsupporters' club, welcomed Fletcher's
OL,17,Fapology."We hope Jack learns from this
OL,18,Fand grows as a person and a player,"
OL,19,Fit read.
OL,26,@yD@IOUzD@dO]
